&none    KRA(A)        &none               KRA(S)         &none            &none             &none            KRA(N)          KRA(E)           &none              KRA(O)           &none
&none    KRA(Z)        KRA(X)              KRA(C)         &none            &none             &none            &none           &none            &none              &kp APOS         &none
