&none    &kp LGUI      &kp LCTRL           &kp LALT       &kp LSHFT        &kp K_APP         &kp N6           &kp N7          &kp N8           &kp N9             &kp N0           &none
&none    &none         &none               &kp RALT       &none            &none             &kp EQUAL        &kp PLUS        &kp MINUS        &kp UNDER          &none            &none
