&none    &kp SLASH     &kp PERIOD          &kp COMMA      &kp APOS         &kp SEMI          &none            &kp LBKT        &kp LBRC         &kp RBKT           &kp RBRC         &none
                       KL_ESC              KL_SPC         KL_TAB           &none             &none            KL_ENT          &kp GRAVE        &kp TILDE
